        <remark xml:id="ve1-rmk-ijk">
            <p>

                The unit vector <m>\textbf{i}</m> is the vector whose first component 1 and all others are 0, <m>\textbf{j}</m> is the one whose second component is 1 with all others 0, and <m>\textbf{k}</m> is the one whose third component is 1 with all others 0.
            </p>
        </remark>

